               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Series IV consists of scrapbooks, clippings, printed ephemera, and sketches. Scrapbooks and clippings relate chiefly to Perkins's political campaigns and activity. Printed ephemera includes brochures and broadsides relating to Perkins. Sketches are pencil studies of shapes, signed "Perkins." Also included is a printed version of a speech by Charles E. Travers.</p>
            </scopecontent>
